quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  94,1,Did We not relieve the tightness in your chest
  94,2,and lift your burden
  94,3,that weighed heavily on your back
  94,4,and raised high your reputation
  94,5,"For truly, with hardship comes ease"
  94,6,"Indeed, with hardship comes ease"
  94,7,"So, when you are done, get ready for serious devotion"
  94,8,and focus all your attention on your Lord